channel.title: Project C-11 || Final release, all dupes fixed, combat neet'end up
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://img194.imageshack.us/img194/7592/pc11.png[/img]
Download source: [url=http://dl.dropbox.com/u/12213315/C-11%20source%20%282%29.zip]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/12213315/C-11%20source%20%282%29.zip[/url]
Download client:[url=http://dl.dropbox.com/u/12213315/C-11%20ClientReFact.zip]http://dl.dropbox.com/u/12213315/C-11%20ClientReFact.zip[/url]
This is release (3) What has been fixed from (1) ---> (2)? -Login All HeadIcons appear for no reason. -Mage Timers Are Now Correct, Have Fun Bridding? :P -Combat Formula Tweeked (Non-Specs) -Specials Have Been Correct You Can Actually Kill Someone With A Spec Now -Teleports Added With Renaming. (E.g Rock Crabs) -Abit More, Can't Really Remember, You'll See As You Test It.
Now your probably saying the thread is the same? actually yes it is. But the following has been done in this. Not much but oh well.
- Around 8 dupe fixes? In the previous sources I never botherd because it was just a small project. Consists of Duel, Bank, Trade and so on... Something about dropping also that my friend did so credit to: Jake my msn friend. For finding a dupe.
- Combat is now a normal nice combat, no overpowering fucken prayers, had to re-write some formulas. - Range is a little better. Thats it (:
Info below, is from my release on R - S, just read it, thats all the servers has.
